Requirements:
        - swig
        - python-dev
        - numpy
        - libhdf5-*-dev
        - libhdf5-*

To install:
        python setup.py install

To build in-place and test:
        python setup.py build
        export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:`echo $PWD/build/lib*` # just a way to add build/lib-platform/
        cd test
        python example.py

To regenerate the docstrings and doxygen documentation, you need to install doxygen, and run
        make clean
        make docstrings.i
